                            office from 1929 to 1950, is mentioned in several places (cf. <locus target="#90rb"/> and <locus target="#129vb"/>). 
                            The manuscript also carries a note and an ex libris by <persName ref="PRS3182ContiRo" role="owner"/> 
                            (cf. <ref target="#e1"/> and <ref target="#e2"/>. Therefore, it can be ascertained, that the manuscript was written 
                            <origDate notBefore="1929" notAfter="1949">between 1929 and 1949</origDate>.
                        </origin>
                        <provenance>The manuscript was in possession of a church in ‘Arbambà’ in <placeName ref="LOC5597Sawa"/>, possibly
                            corresponding to <placeName ref="LOC1516ArbaAm"/> (see <ref target="#e1"/>). The owner of the manuscript 
                            (<persName ref="PRS15443WaldaMadh" role="owner">Walda Madḫǝn</persName>) was named in the manuscript 
                            on <locus target="#11ra"/> et passim.</provenance>
